{"tid":1841722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家幫手減輕醫護既工作量","createTime":"2020-01-25T11:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T15:30:10.000Z","uid":78392,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"335d0448b9c0a661289553c72bbf9e4e96fe3a0e","tid":1841722,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.</span></span>唔好call白車<br />\n改為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">call警車</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xuvtdu5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxuvtdu5.png&h=7c57a4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n知唔知call白車浪費幾多醫護人員<br />\n警察要有義務保護市民，逮捕所有疑似病患者<br />\n如果係屋企發現有武漢肺炎病癥<br />\n記得call警車話有人打鬥<br />\n（打鬥嘅原因就係有人拒絕入院）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/武漢肺炎-據報一名確診病人丈夫感染-料成本港第五個案-夫婦涉昨晚從醫院逃走/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%88%E5%A4%AB%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93-%E6%96%99%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%E6%B6%89%E6%98%A8%E6%99%9A%E5%BE%9E%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%80%83%E8%B5%B0%2F&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=ee40c68b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%88%E5%A4%AB%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93-%E6%96%99%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88-%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6%E6%B6%89%E6%98%A8%E6%99%9A%E5%BE%9E%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%80%83%E8%B5%B0%2F&h=9f23f5b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/武漢肺炎-據報一名確診病人丈夫感染-料成本港第五個案-夫婦涉昨晚從醫院逃走/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.</span></span>行動方便嘅話，自行到警署報案<br />\n報案嘅時候記得除口罩講嘢<br />\n因為係高官教戴口罩係唔可以講嘢㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等警察叔叔帶你入醫院<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.</span></span>到中環等有高級診所嘅地方檢查<br />\n等呢啲可能係接待高官或者有錢佬嘅醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫你檢查左先再送你入醫院<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">手足不是condom</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">抗爭永不終止</span></span>"},{"pid":"c25236e654e5a8628e11f8cc0e20b2495ee5c062","tid":1841722,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:09:50.000Z","msg":"抗爭唔會因為支那肺炎而完結"},{"pid":"7e7b0a1c6b05f7c0e8d22b69b3033edbab22aaa1","tid":1841722,"uid":135334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:09:57.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a0f64afee9c1951ec9e374482cef54d748e77766","tid":1841722,"uid":329466,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:10:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>醫護你咪繼續攬住個光環唔罷工 拉埋200萬個手足陪葬 但見到梓樂彥霖你唔好話係手足呀 你唔撚配呀 烈士為香港付出自己生命 你就為所謂光環去救大陸狗!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"682e05984f8436c4652d7e2b01873274db01c20d","tid":1841722,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:10:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d501719a06b3cde25c5e451bd0b87a076ee5d758","tid":1841722,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光</span></span>"},{"pid":"4ac374377fbe68a69947c53818c2453ef56b1e29","tid":1841722,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d501719a06b3cde25c5e451bd0b87a076ee5d758","tid":1841722,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\